---
---
<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-left">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <h1 class="text-reveal visible">
				<span class="block serif">Estética</span>
				<span class="block serif italic">Vero</span>
			</h1>
            <p class="fade-up visible" style="transition-delay: 0.4s">El arte de revelar tu esencia. Un espacio de lujo dedicado al cuidado femenino en tu ciudad.</p>
            <div class="fade-up visible badge" style="transition-delay: 0.6s">★ 4.9 • 181 Reseñas</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-right fade-up visible" style="transition-delay: 0.2s">
        <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="/images/salon.png" alt="Salón interior Estética Vero" fetchpriority="high" width="800" height="1000" />
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<style>
.hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding-top: 120px;
}
.hero-left {
    padding: 2rem 5%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    order: 2;
}
.hero-right {
    padding: 0 5%;
    order: 1;
}
.image-wrapper {
    height: 60vh;
    width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
}
.image-wrapper img {
    height: 100%;
    width: 100%;
    object-position: center;
}
h1 {
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 15vw, 10rem);
    line-height: 0.8;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -2px;
}
.block { display: block; }
.italic {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
    padding-left: 10%;
    text-transform: none;
}
.hero-text p {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    max-width: 400px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #666;
}
.badge {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    display: inline-block;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--text-dark);
    padding-bottom: 0.2rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
}
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .hero { flex-direction: row; padding-top: 0; }
    .hero-left { width: 55vw; height: 100vh; order: 1; padding-left: 5vw; }
    .hero-right { width: 45vw; height: 100vh; order: 2; padding: 0; }
    .image-wrapper { height: 100vh; }
    .hero-text { position: relative; z-index: 10; margin-top: -10vh; }
}
</style>
